      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is a total gem\u2014it\u2019s been kept in absolutely pristine, showroom condition and drives like a dream. I've babied it since day one, always keeping it garaged and sparkling clean. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that looks and feels brand new, you\u2019ve found it! It\u2019s seriously in tip-top shape. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to tell you more about it!",
