      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality masterpiece that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original factory luster. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the dashboard and trim pieces are free of any UV damage or scratches. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions precisely as intended. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history documented from day one. It rides on premium tires with deep tread and includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that drives as perfectly as it looks.",
